Title: Delver's Call: Fungal Folly
Description:
We've got more reports of fungarians returning to a place we've dubbed "Fungal Folly."

Support is needed to clear these mushroom menaces out of the area to avoid them spreading any further.
ObjectivesText: Complete the Fungal Folly delve on any difficulty.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Meet Bondaz in the Crossroads Plaza.
CompletionText: Are you the one who grabbed the task for Fungal Folly?
RewardText: Thank you for dealing with the fungarians. One day they won't be such a malfunction in our systems.

Objectives.Text: Fungal Folly delve completed on any difficulty
